{
  "stem": "12447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only war that I knew-- that I was reading some small books.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I liked adventure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I read about World War I a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wasn't really that much interested in that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I can't recall too much until the actual fact of the-- of the war came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I seen soldiers being concentrated in our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a lot of soldiers, Polish soldiers, camping out in the streets with their motorcycles, camping out in the park.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So actually, it wasn't the park-- it was the-- where we lived was quite a few empty lots over there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they were putting up their camps over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was, like, more and more soldiers in the-- in the neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you could see some of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cars coming in with soldiers, and artillery with horses moving in because most of the time, the horses would pull the cannons, what I've seen.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To me, it was really exciting to see all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they warned me that this is not fun, that this might be leading to a war, which I actually didn't understand what this whole thing meant.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The first day of war, I remember I was sitting and watching the window, looking out through the window.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I've seen a, a plane in the sky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was another, another plane chasing him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father, at that time, actually was sitting by my next-door neighbor, Dombrowski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were chatting about the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was talking about the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I heard shooting in the sky from these two planes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I came and I told that to the people, they thought I'm kind of fantasizing about the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
